{% extends '_z_index.html.njk' %}

{% block description %}
The red box should be painted before the blue box.

The red and boxes are stacked onto the root layer and the z-index of the red box is less than the
blue box's one.
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<div class="abs blue" style="z-index: 0">
  <div class="fixed red" style="z-index: -1"></div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
